'''Oliver Cockford''' (July 30, 1972 - April 27, 2024) was an American journalist and actor from St. Louis. 

==Early life and education==
Oliver was born in St. Louis to photographer Alyssa Cockford (1941 - 2022) and stay-at-home dad DeAndre Cockford (1941 - 2014).

